      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "It sounds like you're experiencing a sense of frustration and helplessness, feeling like you're constantly putting in effort to fix problems that may be fundamentally unfixable. This can be a draining and demotivating experience, especially when you feel like you're repeating the same cycle over and over. Recognizing that sometimes, things are truly broken beyond what you can repair, can be a tough but ultimately liberating step. Trying to let go and accept that some things may be outside of your control can be a starting point for finding peace.",
